{"tid":2128964,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林鄭最新民望28.9分 近半數人比零分 鍾劍華：等於全面否定","createTime":"2020-07-28T09:36:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-29T12:12:17.000Z","uid":258208,"like":578,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":134,"replies":[{"pid":"3fcd4151edaad3f683dae7e4ffd332481270d4fc","tid":2128964,"uid":258208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T09:36:00.000Z","msg":"（獨媒特約報導）香港民意研究所今日（7月28日）公布最新特首及特區政府民望數字，以及社會狀況評價，結果顯示特首林鄭月娥最新評分為28.9分，當中47%受訪者給予零分，民望淨值則為-53%。香港民意研究所名譽總監鍾劍華認為，給予零分的市民等於全面否定林鄭，除非未來出現戲劇性發展，否則評分難有大轉變。<br />\n<br />\n全文：<a href=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1075913\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1075913&d=oFI5KSBgBGvHra6dYUznBjvkInyplymEwWc8t9jwBTE%3D&h=dfc37df5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1075913&h=b4f1d116\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1075913</a>"},{"pid":"624704617066287e420e4e862ce9cc081d050ea0","tid":2128964,"uid":103230,"like":173,"dislike":15,"score":158,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T09:39:32.000Z","msg":"即係仲有5成人俾50分左右<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee868a6d6597b17922dc9781bf5c7bc8ed018dd6","tid":2128964,"uid":325243,"like":247,"dislike":3,"score":244,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T09:40:18.000Z","msg":"唔好鬆懈<br />\n今年年頭係得20左右<br />\n而家就快30"},{"pid":"f8f1169e398f985456b0260a111ab5d5666af086","tid":2128964,"uid":255637,"like":57,"dislike":0,"score":57,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T09:41:59.000Z","msg":"無得俾負 先零分姐"},{"pid":"8d774839a3d6a6b8b4d83d262e1741595e77d93e","tid":2128964,"uid":54959,"like":121,"dislike":3,"score":118,"quote":{"pid":"ee868a6d6597b17922dc9781bf5c7bc8ed018dd6","tid":2128964,"uid":325243,"like":247,"dislike":3,"score":244,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T09:40:18.000Z","msg":"唔好鬆懈<br />\n今年年頭係得20左右<br />\n而家就快30"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"202